{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now that Friday night when I couldn't go out and my parents, of course, were frightened and dumbfounded and whatnot-- and when you're really frightened, you tend to do insignificant things, dumb things.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've seen people running back into burning houses literally to bring out a jar of preserves, you know, I mean, you sometimes lose your sense of priorities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my-- we had lots of books and bookcases and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had to go through all the books to make sure we didn't have Karl Marx, or whatever, that could get us into trouble.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't think of hiding some money, some jewelery, or God knows what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still don't know what I would do, probably just sit back and say, this is fate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we ransacked the library.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my parents, as I said, they were collectors of art pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had these vitrines, these glass cabinets, with delicate things in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother had, among other things, something 17th, 18th century, 18th century, 19th century, little silver revolver which had no bullets and couldn't shoot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was the handiwork, the, the engraving that was so precious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole thing was maybe four, five inches long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So with Karl Marx and some other things and that silver revolver, we were going to get rid of that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And by then, it was night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother had the very wide coat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did they call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Steamer coats or travel coats, you know, one of those voluminous, very elegant coats.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we decided under this coat, you could hide anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we are going to go to a park and get rid of this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so Mama and I traipsed out in the middle of the night to a park.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
